translation[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif â€“laam-raa yeh kitab-e-elahi ki aayaten hain aur khullay aur roshan quran ki
  15,2,Woh bhi waqt hoga kay kafir apney musalman honey ki aarzoo keren gay
  15,3,Aap unhen khata nafa uthata aur (jhooti) umeedon mein masghool hota chor dijiye yeh khud abhi jaan len gay
  15,4,Kissi basti ko hum ney halak nahi kiya magar yeh kay uss kay liye muqarrar navishta tha
  15,5,Koi giroh apni maut say na aagay barhta hai na peechay rehta hai
  15,6,Enhon ney kaha aey woh shaks jiss per quran utara gaya hai yaqeenan tu to koi deewana hai
  15,7,Agar tu sacha hi hai to humaray pass farishton ko kiyon nahi laata
  15,8,Hum farishton ko haq kay sath hi utartay hain aur uss waqt woh mohlat diye gaye nahi hotay
  15,9,Hum ney iss quran ko nazil farmaya hai aur hum hi uss kay mohafiz hain
  15,10,Hum ney aap say pehlay agli ummaton mein bhi apney rasool (barabar) bhejay
  15,11,Aur (lekin) jo bhi rasool aata woh uss ka mazaq uratay
  15,12,Gunehgaron kay dilon mein hum issi tarah yehi racha diya kertay hain
  15,13,Woh iss per eman nahi latay aur yaqeenan aglon ka tareeqa guzra hua hai
  15,14,Aur agar hum inn per aasman ka darwaza khol bhi den aur yeh wahan charhney bhi lag jayen
  15,15,Tab bhi yehi kahen gay humari nazar bandi ker di gaee hai bulkay hum logon per jadoo ker diya gaya hai